# Platform icon variants we don't ship at this slice (regenerable via
# `npx tauri icon src-tauri/icons/icon.png` from a source 1024x1024).
# We commit ONLY the canonical icon.png + macOS icon.icns + Windows
# icon.ico + the three desktop sizes (32 / 128 / 128@2x). Android +
# iOS + Windows-Store icons are forward-substrate.
icons/64x64.png
icons/Square*.png
icons/StoreLogo.png
icons/android/
icons/ios/

